gulf arab deputi oil minist to meet in bahrain deputi oil minist from six gulf arab state will meet in bahrain today to discuss coordin of crude oil market , the offici emir news agenc wam report . wam said the offici would be discuss implement of last sunday 's agreement in doha by gulf cooper council ( gcc ) oil minist to help each other market their crude oil . four of the gcc state - saudi arabia , the unit arab emir ( uae ) , kuwait and qatar - are member of the organia of petroleum export countri ( opec ) and some face stiff buyer resist to offici opec price .